data.description: 2 Bedrooms & 2 Full Bath Patio home in 55+ Neighborhood.  Very effecient use of space makes this home comfortable and manageable. Master features private master bath with walk-in shower and walk-in closet. Master bath is fully handicap accessible. Open floorplan, 36 inch handicap accessible doors throughout, make movement easier. High celings, gas fireplace, convenient location. New paint in all rooms. Washer and Dryer included. New dishwasher. Outdoor Storage room. Fenced backyard. Neighborhood features walking paths and a gorgeous community Clubhouse with workout room, party and event space, Deck with gas grill and plenty of community events. Regime fee covers all electrical, gas, cable, water/sewer, trash pick-up, yard maintenance (outside fence), Cable TV, Clubhouse (including electricity), Common area maintenance, Road maintenance, Sidewalk maintenance and Green areas. Regime fee also incudes HVAC filter change twice per year and Smoke detector battery change twice per year.  Neighborhood-wide Video Security System. No Refrigerator, Ring Doorbell will not convey.
